c: 7
v: 77
t: "Then (without enduring any longer to see her as evidence of the truth of Salih’s message), they cruelly slaughtered the she-camel, and disdainfully disobeyed the command of their Lord, and said: \"O Salih! Bring upon us that (punishment) with which you have threatened us, if you are of those sent (by God with the truth)"